    "TitleKey": "Intersec_ShipWaveAttack_DrawOutBoss_S_Title_001",
    "DisplayTitle": "Eradicate UEE Threat: [TargetName]",
    "Description": "MISSION SPECS\n\nArea of Operation: ~mission(Location|Address)\nHostile Forces: Outlaws\nEquipment Specs: Capital Ship\nBriefing: An outlaw fleet lead by <EM4>~mission(TargetName)</EM4> has been planning a potentially devastating strike against sensitive UEE targets. InterSec has been tasked with dealing with this threat before their attack can be launched.\n\nAfter putting together a fighting force of your own, head to the site and engage with the hostiles there. Their leader will not risk entering into the fray themselve unless they feel their operation is suitably at risk. Stay at the site and take out hostile targets, until you can engage with the groups leader directly and put a stop to this heinous attack once and for all.\n\nRespectfully, \n\nDeacon Tobin \nOperations Manager \nInterSec Defense Solutions  \n\nThis communication consists of a non-binding offer that upon acceptance may be immediately terminated by either party without any given notice. All operations are conducted at the contractor\u2019s own personal risk and must adhere to system law where applicable.",
